      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUDDY BRILLIANCE (8) comes off a brave performance last time out when he drew a similar barrier and worked but stuck on for fourth, beaten less than 3m. Tactics will be crucial from this draw but he is a leading hope if things go his way. SHE THE DEVIL (3) will find this easier than her last attempt in the Regional Championships State Final at Menangle and should enjoy a lovely run having come from a similar barrier to win at this circuit and distance last month. FOREVER ONTHE PUNT (9) hasn't been far away in any of his three starts since a spell and should be peaking now. Finished fifth at his latest appearance at Wagga after coming from this row to place at Coolamon. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon and he is proven at this circuit and distance. SLYX NZ (2) can be competitive from the low draw.",
